OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,GIf you are an observant Freesat viewer
OL,7,Gyou may have noticed a little change
OL,8,Gin the past few days.
OL,10,FThe SD versions of BBC channels
OL,11,Ffinally disappeared off the electronic
OL,12,Fprogramme guide on HD boxes ` months
OL,13,Fafter they became completely redundant.
OL,15,FAll BBC national and regional services
OL,16,Fhave, of course, been available in HD
OL,17,Fon satellite for about 9 months.
OL,19,FThe SD signal was left on for the
OL,20,Fbenefit of those still using SD
OL,21,Fequipment but will finally be switched
OL,22,Foff on 8th January.
