OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThis is a reminder that the BBC has
OL,7,Fbeen exceptionally cautious to try to
OL,8,Fensure nobody is disadvantaged.
OL,10,FThe BBC could have shut down its SD
OL,11,Fservices months ago ` or at least
OL,12,Fremoved them from HD boxes completely.
OL,14,FWhat may look like overcaution has a
OL,15,Fvery good and entirely laudable
OL,16,Fexplanation.
OL,18,FThe public service broadcaster cannot
OL,19,Frisk excluding the elderly, the
OL,20,Fvulnerable and the disadvantaged.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
