OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FFor most of us, the red button text
OL,7,Fservice may simply seem like a
OL,8,Fnostalgic reminder of Ceefax. In fact,
OL,9,Fplans to shut it were delayed during
OL,10,Fthe early days of covid and seem to
OL,11,Fhave been quietly abandoned.
OL,13,FI am beginning to wonder if plans to
OL,14,Fmake BBC Four online only may be set
OL,15,Ffor the long grass too. This is
OL,16,Fcurrently expected in 2025 but no date
OL,17,Fhas been confirmed.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
