OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FBBC Four is now principally an archive
OL,7,Fchannel ` a place to find content
OL,8,Fwhich also appears in curated
OL,9,Fcollections and box sets on the
OL,10,FiPlayer. Yet it remains one of the
OL,11,Fmost watched digital channels at a
OL,12,Frelatively modest cost.
OL,14,FSome who do not have access to iPlayer
OL,15,F(at least on their TV) would certainly
OL,16,Fmiss it.
OL,18,FIt is also worth noting that no date
OL,19,Fhas been announced for the closure of
OL,20,FRadio 4 Long Wave even though long
OL,21,Fwave will soon carry a full simulcast
OL,22,Fof the main FM/Digital service.
