OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThe services affected include Downtown
OL,7,FRadio in Northern Ireland and Greatest
OL,8,FHits Radio in Scotland. GHR's Scottish
OL,9,Ffrequencies were the original homes of
OL,10,Fthe likes of Radio Clyde and Radio
OL,11,FForth.
OL,13,FThe company is acting swiftly and has
OL,14,Fclearly concluded that the negatives
OL,15,Fof an AM licence now exceed the
OL,16,Fbenefits. It will be busy encouraging
OL,17,FGHR listeners to go digital in the
OL,18,Fcoming weeks.
OL,20,FBut to expect the BBC to do the same
OL,21,Fquickly is misplaced.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/8
