OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThe public service broadcaster must be
OL,7,Fjudged by a different measure.
OL,9,FLooking at its caution on SD satellite
OL,10,Fand the Red Button text service, it
OL,11,Funderstands the need to help those who
OL,12,Fcould easily be left behind even if
OL,13,Fmaintaining a particular service makes
OL,14,Fno simple economic sense.
OL,16,FAnd yet again let's say this loudly,
OL,17,Fas if we needed to. Linear BBC TV is
OL,18,Fnot going anywhere anytime soon.
